	(text "Note: \nW/o DCR -> Resonant Circuit\n		-> f_o = 1 / (2*pi*sqrt(L*C))\n\nCutoff Frequency, fc = 1591549.430919[Hz]\n				  = ~1.6MHz\n				  Q =  0.67\nCalc using:\nhttp://sim.okawa-denshi.jp/en/CRlowkeisan.htm\nWhy: To eliminate High Frequency Noise\n     Steeper Roll-Off than Convential LPF\nRmb: DC Power Supply is never perfect"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 25.908 94.742 0)
